This mailing list is for Bioconductor package development and Bioconductor submissions not CRAN.

Bioconductor only allows dependencies from CRAN or Bioconductor and does not allow github only repositories.

If you indeed meant to submit to CRAN you should check with CRAN's submission policies on what they allow:
https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/policies.html




